- medium term persistence recovery
  - graceful shutdown including persistence sync flushing and completion
- long term persistence recover
  - inverted snarked ledger witness queue tracked by persistent root
  - steps to recover
    - recover snarked ledger at persistent frontier root by applying undos from queue
    - build persistent frontier root staged ledger from persistent frontier root snarked ledger and root data
    - apply diffs from persistent frontier path to persistent root to newly constructed staged ledger, moving persistent root as you go
    - persist new staged ledger auxiliary information
    - load full frontier from persistent frontier
